snippet.title: Mario Party Custom Boards - F3 2021 Showcase Trailer
snippet.description:
The Mario Party 1-3 custom board and event modding scene continues to grow and we've got hundreds of neat boards and events up for download. This trailer, featured in F3 2021, showcases 10 boards uploaded within the last year. 

Join our Discord community for up to date support and a place to share board and event ideas: https://discord.com/invite/BQMuUpM

Other important Links:

Mario Party Legacy | https://mariopartylegacy.com/
PartyPlanner64 Editor | http://partyplanner64.github.io/PartyPlanner64/
Custom Boards Downloads Database | http://www.mariopartylegacy.com/forum/index.php?action=downloads

Thank you to everyone that has already submitted boards, events, and music but especially to those whose boards and events were featured in the video. Music by The Noble Demon.
